==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wagoner
<hw>Wag"on*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
conducts a wagon; one whose business it is to drive a wagon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>The constellation Charles's
Wain, or Ursa Major. See <cref>Ursa major</cref>, under
<er>Ursa</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wagonette</ent>⟦br⟧
